These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, water, tea
4 different pets are kept: dog, snake, guinea-pig, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, roller, bus, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person drinking juice is the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | milk  | tea | water    | juice       |
| Pet         | snake | pony    | guinea-pig      | dog |
| Transport   | train   | bus | roller | motorbike        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pineapple, lime, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, scientist, software-developer, teacher
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, bus, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the person eating lime##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the pilot##1
6. the person driving the scooter is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | lime   | pineapple | avocado     | cucumber      |
| Job         | scientist | software-developer | teacher | pilot |
| Transport   | subway    | scooter   | bus     | jet-ski      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, skydiving, camping, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, funk, house, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, german, polish, thai
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the german is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of house##1
5. the thai is on the right of the fan of funk##1
6. the thai is on the right of the polish##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | drawing | skydiving | camping | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | funk    | indie | house     |
| Nationality   | italian | polish    | thai | german    |

