.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, journalist, designer, scientist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse, weightlifting, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, bike, scooter
1. the designer is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the journalist is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is the designer##1
7. the designer is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
8. the scientist is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | security-guard | scientist | designer | journalist |
| Sport       | lacrosse     | sailing      | parkour     | weightlifting      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car         | scooter      | bike        |

