.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, hiking, card-games, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, comedy, animation, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, weightlifting, cricket, soccer
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | card-games   | chess | hiking  | reading      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | drama        | superhero  | comedy       |
| Sport         | cycling | cricket    | weightlifting | soccer |

