.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, fisherman, bartender, photographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, crime, comedy, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, d&b, punk, ambient
1. the security-guard is the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the photographer##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
5. the fisherman is on the far left##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is the bartender##1
7. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
8. the photographer is the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | fisherman | bartender | photographer | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | comedy  | crime | zombie   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | soul     | punk | d&b       |

