.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, peach, apricot, kale
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, card-games, hiking, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, zombie, sports, superhero
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
2. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is the person eating apricot##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | pomegranate  | kale | apricot   | peach     |
| Hobby         | dancing | card-games   | magic-tricks  | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | sports         | drama  | zombie | superhero  |

