.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, mirinda, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, time-travel, martial-arts, family
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, indian, russian, chinese
1. the person drinking fanta is the russian##1
2. the chinese is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the russian##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the chinese is the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the indian is on the left of the chinese##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee | mirinda     | hot-chocolate | fanta |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | disaster | martial-arts       | time-travel    |
| Nationality   | indian   | chinese | brazilian    | russian |

