.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, papaya, cranberry, lemon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, country, electronic, funk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rugby, ice-hockey, swimming
1. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person eating papaya##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the fan of funk##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | cranberry        | lemon   | papaya  | eggplant   |
| Music-Genre   | rock         | funk     | country    | electronic       |
| Sport         | rugby | handball | ice-hockey | swimming |

