.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, coffee, water
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kale, grapes, eggplant
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, snake, goat
1. the person drinking water is the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating kale##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
7. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | tea    | coffee | water | sprite        |
| Food       | eggplant | broccoli  | kale | grapes     |
| Pet        | horse    | snake   | goat  | cat |

