.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, teacher, scientist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, climbing, surfing, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, taxi, train, subway
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the lawyer##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the left of the scientist##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person driving the train##1
8. the person who's sport is surfing is the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | fisherman  | scientist | lawyer  | teacher |
| Sport       | surfing | climbing        | sailing | skateboarding       |
| Transport   | boat   | taxi          | subway          | train       |

