.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, collecting, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, epic, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indian, british, nigerian
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the nigerian is on the left of the dutch##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the british##1
7. the nigerian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks   | collecting   | puzzles | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | thriller | martial-arts   | spy |
| Nationality   | nigerian     | dutch  | british  | indian  |

