3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the fan of funk##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping | collecting    | video-games        | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | folk     | hip-hop        | funk   |
| Sport         | badminton   | handball | cycling | cricket  |

