3. the egyptian is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the italian##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
8. the japanese is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | crime  | family    | martial-arts    |
| Nationality   | chinese | italian  | egyptian  | japanese |
| Transport     | subway  | snowmobile | jet-ski | tram        |

