4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person watching animation movies##1
8. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
