4. the fan of soul is the german##1
5. the manager is on the far left##1
6. the nurse is on the right of the australian##1
7. the pakistani is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | manager  | paramedic | entrepreneur  | nurse |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | pop       | dubstep | indie      |
| Nationality   | german | american  | australian    | pakistani    |

