4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish | canadian | pakistani |
| Sport         | soccer | ice-hockey | badminton  | climbing  |
| Transport     | bus  | bike | taxi     | scooter  |

