.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking, board-games, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, police-officer, pilot, security-guard
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, jet-ski, train
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the security-guard##1
3. the pilot is on the right of the security-guard##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the police-officer##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the writer##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | hiking | skydiving | board-games |
| Job         | writer | police-officer  | security-guard   | pilot      |
| Transport   | skateboard        | jet-ski  | train   | bike         |

