.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, chef, fisherman, manager
There are 4 different nationalities: german, italian, american, british
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, rowing, baseball
1. the chef is on the left of the german##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
4. the american is on the far right##1
5. the german is the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the british is on the far left##1
7. the manager is on the far right##1
8. the british is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | chef  | fisherman  | teacher | manager |
| Nationality   | british   | german | italian   | american      |
| Sport         | climbing | rowing    | surfing   | baseball         |

 